
Content
-------
CMSIS - Cortex Microcontroller Software Interface Standard Library for ST Cortex M3 Processor
STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver - STM32F10x Standard Peripherals Library from ST

Version
--------
V3.1.2

Installation
------------

Just run "sudo sh install.sh"

Alternative (for other path): 
1. Install CMSIS:
> cd CMSIS
> make
> sudo make install

2. Install STM32:
> cd STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver
> make
> sudo make install


The default gcc toolchain is arm-elf, and default install directory is
/opt/gnuarm. If you want to use a different settings you can use the prefix and arch_prefix
variables. For example:

> prefix=/usr/mydir arch_prefix=arm-elf make
> prefix=/usr/mydir arch_prefix=arm-elf make install


Link
----------------
www.st.com/STM32
